---
title: Seared Salmon 'Sushi' Bowl with Avocado & Wasabi Mayo
description: All the flavour of a sushi roll but all loaded into a wholesome bowl - from the tasty rice, succulent salmon, crunchy cucumber and creamy avocado, all topped off with a generous drizzle of warming wasabi mayo… this dish will give your local sushi train a run for its money.
